 \"from\": 976, \"to\": 982}, {\"ngram\": \"a public holiday\", \"from\": 1001, \"to\": 1017}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Could we have a day off to celebrate?\\\"\", \"from\": 1020, \"to\": 1059, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a day\", \"from\": 1035, \"to\": 1040}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sunrise host Matt Shirvington asked.\", \"from\": 1060, \"to\": 1096, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1073, \"end\": 1089, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Shirvington\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Matt Shirvington\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Shirvington\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Shirvington\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr Albanese laughed it off and told Shirvington to \\\"negotiate\\\" with management.\", \"from\": 1098, \"to\": 1177, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1101, \"end\": 1109, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Albanese\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Albanese\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Albanese\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Albanese\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Shirvington\", \"from\": 1134, \"to\": 1145}, {\"ngram\": \"management\", \"from\": 1166, \"to\": 1176}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Certainly there are many Australians who will be pretty tired after the last couple of weeks because they have been engaged with our athletes,\\\" the Labor leader said.\", \"from\": 1179, \"to\": 1346, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1328, \"end\": 1333, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Labor_Party\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6608237515940438e-14, \"text\": \"Labor\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Labor_Party\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Labor_Party\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"many Australians\", \"from\": 1200, \"to\": 1216}, {\"ngram\": \"the last couple\", \"from\": 1248, \"to\": 1263}, {\"ngram\": \"weeks\", \"from\": 1267, \"to\": 1272}, {\"ngram\": \"our athletes\", \"from\": 1309, \"to\": 1321}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And the thing about these Olympians as well, it's important to remember, is that for so many of them, they get by on not much income at all.\", \"from\": 1348, \"to\": 1489, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these Olympians\", \"from\": 1369, \"to\": 1384}, {\"ngram\": \"not much income\", \"from\": 1466, \"to\": 1481}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They are not receiving the sort of salaries we see our... rugby league or AFL players receive.\", \"from\": 1491, \"to\": 1586, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sort\", \"from\": 1515, \"to\": 1523}, {\"ngram\": \"salaries\", \"from\": 1527, \"to\": 1535}, {\"ngram\": \"rugby league or AFL players\", \"from\": 1550, \"to\": 1577}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They do it out of their joy for their sport (and) their love for their country.\\\"\", \"from\": 1587, \"to\": 1667, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their joy\", \"from\": 1605, \"to\": 1614}, {\"ngram\": \"their sport\", \"from\": 1619, \"to\": 1630}, {\"ngram\": \"their love\", \"from\": 1637, \"to\": 1647}, {\"ngram\": \"their country\", \"from\": 1652, \"to\": 1665}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr Albanese also noted how Australia was constantly \\\"punching way above our weight\\\" in terms of medals won per capita at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1669, \"to\": 1803, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1672, \"end\": 1680, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Albanese\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Albanese\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Albanese\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Albanese\"}, {\"begin\": 1696, \"end\": 1705, \"title\": \"http:/